6
00:00:25,177 --> 00:00:26,038
development of the industry.

7
00:00:26,819 --> 00:00:29,742
Every year, the pace of change accelerates.

8
00:00:30,122 --> 00:00:32,084
More and more really nice stuff happens in the field of

9
00:00:32,144 --> 00:00:32,685
accessibility.

10
00:00:32,705 --> 00:00:35,067
