00:13:51,239 --> 00:13:56,001
So blog posts, social media, even like mainstream media articles about it.

252
00:13:57,422 --> 00:14:00,003
From gamers, from developers, from advocacy groups,

253
00:14:00,424 --> 00:14:02,264
people like American Foundation for the Blind,

254
00:14:02,485 --> 00:14:04,265
groups that are not normally involved in gaming

