00:14:27,307 --> 00:14:28,267
compared to a couple of years ago

264
00:14:28,287 --> 00:14:29,248
about what games should be,

265
00:14:29,528 --> 00:14:30,449
about what games should be doing.

266
00:14:32,610 --> 00:14:33,791
And it's also really significant

267
00:14:33,811 --> 00:14:37,693
because it's a big sign of the cultural significance of games.

268
00:14:39,018 --> 00:14:42,259
Because there's a really, really strong undercurrent to all this commentary

269
00:14:42,879 --> 00:14:45,520
of people who, you know, they could see this cultural phenomenon

270
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:48,281
happening around them, and they didn't want to be excluded from it.

271
00:14:48,721 --> 00:14:51,381
They wanted to experience the same thing that all their friends were experiencing.

272
00:14:55,162 --> 00:14:57,603
Now the other thing that's been dominating, obviously, the games press

273
00:14:57,643 --> 00:15:00,444
