274
00:15:02,945 --> 00:15:05,525
And VR can be quite an exclusionary platform.

275
00:15:07,646 --> 00:15:09,467
So the requirements to be able to walk around a room,

276
00:15:10,168 --> 00:15:14,150
the requirements to be able to use two hand-controlled motion

277
00:15:14,190 --> 00:15:18,473
tracking controllers, even just the simple function

278
00:15:18,493 --> 00:15:21,275
of putting a large, bulky object onto your head,

