00:16:00,798 --> 00:16:01,758
touch controls came out.

293
00:16:02,759 --> 00:16:05,581
So it's really, really exciting to see just this

294
00:16:05,601 --> 00:16:08,262
kind of level of understanding and appreciation of

295
00:16:08,302 --> 00:16:10,224
accessibility at such an early stage of VR.

296
00:16:14,586 --> 00:16:15,967
And we also had to launch a PlayStation VR.

