00:16:17,603 --> 00:16:19,844
Where the vast majority of launch games

298
00:16:19,904 --> 00:16:21,125
had an option like this.

299
00:16:21,785 --> 00:16:23,886
We have a choice between a standard controller

300
00:16:23,986 --> 00:16:24,787
and motion controllers.

301
00:16:25,407 --> 00:16:26,928
Which is obviously handy if you don't happen

302
00:16:26,948 --> 00:16:27,908
to own move controllers.

303
00:16:28,388 --> 00:16:30,409
Also really, really handy if you don't happen

304
00:16:30,449 --> 00:16:33,110
to have a full set of working arms and working fingers.

