00:17:13,350 --> 00:17:15,831
team up, and then have a very, very short amount of time to build a game.

317
00:17:17,819 --> 00:17:20,840
And one of the biggest ones is an event

318
00:17:20,860 --> 00:17:21,740
called Global Game Jam.

