00:17:23,241 --> 00:17:25,682
This is a photo of just one single venue of Global Game

320
00:17:25,702 --> 00:17:25,882
Jam.

321
00:17:25,982 --> 00:17:27,862
There's venues like this all over the world, loads of

322
00:17:27,882 --> 00:17:29,903
different countries, tens of thousands of participants.

323
00:17:34,479 --> 00:17:37,480
