330
00:18:10,336 --> 00:18:12,699
Based on the average team sizes in Global Game Jam,

331
00:18:13,260 --> 00:18:15,683
that's something in the region of 10,000 developers

332
00:18:16,004 --> 00:18:17,666
who were experimenting with accessibility

333
00:18:17,726 --> 00:18:18,687
over the course of this weekend.

334
00:18:24,814 --> 00:18:26,775
And Global Game Jams don't have a monopoly on this either.

335
00:18:27,176 --> 00:18:29,378
In the past year, there's been more accessibility jams

