00:18:40,948 --> 00:18:42,750
Global Game Jams, there's been ones in Poland,

343
00:18:42,910 --> 00:18:44,512
UK, Canada, global ones.

344
00:18:45,873 --> 00:18:47,074
And it's really, really nice to see

345
00:18:47,134 --> 00:18:49,997
because game jams are such a powerful tool

346
00:18:50,057 --> 00:18:51,138
for raising awareness.

