00:21:39,204 --> 00:21:42,106
But what makes Tomb Raider unique is that it's optional.

404
00:21:42,126 --> 00:21:45,267
So there are some people who really, really rely on this

405
00:21:45,307 --> 00:21:45,747
kind of stuff.

406
00:21:46,207 --> 00:21:47,488
Other people who find it distracting.

407
00:21:48,569 --> 00:21:49,389
Just give them the option.

408
00:21:49,509 --> 00:21:50,129
Turn it on and off.

